例如，给出 n = 3，生成结果为：

```
[
  "((()))",
  "(()())",
  "(())()",
  "()(())",
  "()()()"
]
```

var generateParenthesis = function(n) {
  if (n === 0) {
    return []
  }
  let dp = [['']]
  for (let i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
    dp[i] = []
    for (let j = 0; j <= i - 1; j++) {
      let part1 = dp[j]
      let part2 = dp[i - 1 - j]
      for (let k1 = 0; k1 < part1.length; k1++) {
        for (let k2 = 0; k2 < part2.length; k2++) {
          dp[i].push('(' + part1[k1] + ')' + part2[k2])
        }
      }
    }
  }
  return dp[n]
};
